Package de.dosmike.sponge.megamenus.api.elements.concepts

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClickable<X extends IClickable>
    Interface to be implemented by IElements that shall react to inventory clicks
    IElement
    Generic Interface shared by all elements placeable on a IMenu
    IInventory<X extends IInventory>
    Elements that represent a inventory of some kind an can have a slot change
    IPressable<X extends IPressable>
    Interface to be implemented by IElements that shall react to keys being pressed.
    ISizeable
    for Gui Elements that span more than 1 inventory slot.
    IValueChangeable<V,X extends IValueChangeable>
    Default interface to be implemented by elements that can have more than once state, such as checkboxes, spinner, etc
